t: "To God Ë¹aloneËº belongs whatever is in the heavens and whatever is on the earth. Indeed, We have commanded those given the Scripture before you, as well as you, to be mindful of God. But if you disobey, then Ë¹know thatËº to God belongs whatever is in the heavens and the earth. And God is Self-Sufficient, Praiseworthy"